HEADWORD: Ferrugo
<hw>Fer*ru"go</hw> <pr>(f⟦ecr⟧r*r⟦udd⟧"g⟦osl⟧)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[L., iron rust, fr. <ets>ferrum</ets> iron.]</ety> <def>A disease
of plants caused by fungi, commonly called the <altname>rust</altname>,
from its resemblance to iron rust in color.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

